name: KITO - URCORNYVERSE
description: Development sketch for the character KITTO, part of the new upcoming URCORNYVERSE experience launching 01.10.21. KITTO is URCORNY’S imaginary friend. Depending on URCORNY’S mood KITTO changes their colour and helps URCORNY understand how he is feeling. Although invisible to everyone else KITTO can move objects the same as anyone else and they love to cause mischief and play pranks on others in the URCORNYVERSE.
